      <h2>About Taxi Hand Signals</h2>
      <p>Taxi hand signals are essential to South Africa's public transport. They allow commuters to communicate quickly and efficiently to minibus drivers without words.</p>
      <p><strong>Why Important?</strong> Knowing these signals improves safety, reduces misunderstandings, and supports smooth travel.</p>
